% rebase("base.tpl", active="contribute")
<main class="row align-center">
  <section class="small-11 columns">
    <h1>
      <i class="fa fa-medkit"></i>
      Contribute to Pump19
    </h1>
    <p>
      Do you think Pump19 needs a new <dfn>Chem</dfn> (the magic words that power a golem)?
      That can be arranged easily enough.
      Pump19 is built upon <abbr title="Free and open-source software">FOSS</abbr> components and is
      itself released under the <a href="http://opensource.org/licenses/MIT">MIT License</a>.
    </p>
    <p>
      All of Pump19's source code is hosted on <a href="https://github.com/"><i class="fa fa-github"></i>&nbsp;GitHub</a>.
      There you can suggest new features, report issues, or even fork and contribute your own functionality.
    </p>
  </section>
  <section class="small-11 columns">
    <h2>Repositories</h2>
    <p>
      There exist two distinct source code repositories: one for the chat golem itself and one for
      this website.
    </p>
  </section>
  <section class="small-9 medium-5 columns text-center">
    <h3>
      Pump19
      <small>
        <i class="fa fa-comments-o"></i>
        Chat Golem
      </small>
    </h3>
    <div class="stacked button-group">
      <a class="primary button" href="https://github.com/pyrige/pump19">
        <i class="fa fa-code-fork"></i>
        Source Code
      </a>
      <a class="secondary button" href="https://github.com/pyrige/pump19/issues">
        <i class="fa fa-bug"></i>
        Issue Tracker
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="small-9 medium-5 columns text-center">
    <h3>
      Pump19.eu
      <small>
        <i class="fa fa-globe"></i>
        Website
      </small>
    </h3>
    <div class="stacked button-group">
      <a class="primary button" href="https://github.com/pyrige/pump19.eu">
        <i class="fa fa-code-fork"></i>
        Source Code
      </a>
      <a class="secondary button" href="https://github.com/pyrige/pump19.eu/issues">
        <i class="fa fa-bug"></i>
        Issue Tracker
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>
